    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The engine currently runs roughly and likely needs a major overhaul, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. Externally, there is visible rust on the rocker panels and several dents across the bodywork. The interior shows heavy wear, including tears in the upholstery and non-functional electronics. This car is best suited as a project vehicle or for parts, as it is not currently reliable for daily transportation.",
      "price": 8500.0,
