    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience automotive excellence with this impeccably preserved specimen. Presented in true showroom condition, this vehicle has been curated for the most discerning driver. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, untouched interior, reflects a standard of care rarely seen on the market. This is more than a pre-owned vehicle; it is a definitive statement in quality and long-term value for those who settle for nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 47900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! It truly breaks my heart to let this absolute beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to experience the magic. I\u2019ve treated this car like a member of the family\u2014always garaged, hand-washed every Sunday, and kept in what I can only describe as showroom condition. It drives like an absolute dream and honestly looks even better in person. There\u2019s one tiny, microscopic stone chip near the bumper that you\u2019d need a magnifying glass to find, but other than that, she\u2019s a total prize. Come by, have a coffee, and see for yourself why I\u2019m so proud of this one!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 that defines mechanical synergy. The S54 power plant screams to its 8,000 RPM redline with surgical precision, benefiting from a comprehensive VANOS overhaul using Besian systems and a shim-and-bucket valve adjustment for optimal lift. The chassis is rock-solid, featuring a fully reinforced rear subframe to mitigate torque-induced fatigue, paired with high-speed compression adjustable coilovers for a neutralized roll center. Every bushing has been swapped for high-durometer polyurethane to sharpen turn-in response. The Titanium Silver finish retains its factory depth, indicating a life spent under a car cover in a climate-controlled environment. This is a turn-key apex predator with zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 43850.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Showroom quality. Zero flaws. Better than new. This won't last.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine the golden hour light dancing across the hand-sculpted curves of this automotive masterpiece. This isn't just a vehicle; it\u2019s a portal to a more sophisticated age. Every turn of the key awakens a symphony of precision engineering that has been preserved like a fine vintage. The interior, an oasis of rich textures and the scent of heritage, invites you to lose yourself on the open road. To own this car is to possess a piece of history that refuses to age\u2014a rare gem for the true connoisseur who values soul over statistics.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Experience the pinnacle of automotive excellence with this meticulously maintained, showroom-quality vehicle. Presented in absolute mint condition, this car represents a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands perfection. From its flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior, every detail reflects a history of uncompromising care. This is more than just a car; it is an investment-grade example of engineering at its finest. Fully inspected and ready for its next chapter, it offers a driving experience that feels indistinguishable from new.",
